the key to making this whole thing work.

00:02:21.090 --> 00:02:24.090
We announced our translation project
during last year's event

00:02:24.299 --> 00:02:27.149
and at that time we had
30 translations either completed

00:02:27.150 --> 00:02:28.200
or in progress.

00:02:28.740 --> 00:02:31.540
Joni has done a fabulous job
keeping this program rolling

00:02:31.799 --> 00:02:37.229
and as of today we have 77 completed
translations and another 34 in progress.

00:02:37.829 --> 00:02:40.650
If you're interested
in contributing to translations,

00:02:41.009 --> 00:02:47.438
sign up
at https://wpaccessibility.day/translate.

