00:04:10.830 --> 00:04:12.330
Thank you for your generosity.

00:04:13.289 --> 00:04:16.529
Our goal is not only to have
an event about accessibility.

00:04:17.100 --> 00:04:20.970
It's to include people with disabilities
everywhere in the process.

00:04:21.630 --> 00:04:23.880
A key mantra of the disability
rights movement

00:04:23.910 --> 00:04:25.160
is about decision-making.

00:04:25.650 --> 00:04:27.050
Nothing about us without us.

00:04:28.289 --> 00:04:30.689
I don't identify as a person
with a disability,

00:04:31.199 --> 00:04:34.890
and I may be about as far as you can get
in terms of privilege as a white man

00:04:34.890 --> 00:04:37.290
in my late 40s without a disability.

00:04:38.489 --> 00:04:41.139
Including people with disabilities
requires intention.

00:04:41.790 --> 00:04:45.479
We're fortunate that many of our speakers
are also people with disabilities,

00:04:45.479 --> 00:04:48.509
but that good fortune is
the result of hard work to make sure

00:04:48.510 --> 00:04:52.109
that we're using inclusive platforms
and communicating effectively

00:04:52.319 --> 00:04:53.819
at every point in the process.

00:04:54.420 --> 00:04:57.419
One thing we want
to do is always focus on improving.

00:04:57.989 --> 00:05:01.799
Please, don't hesitate to give us feedback
about anything you think

00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:03.100
we could have done better.

00:05:03.269 --> 00:05:04.529
We're all here to learn.

00:05:05.129 --> 00:05:08.529
There's a feedback form linked
in the navigation menu on the website,

00:05:08.730 --> 00:05:11.430
and it will stay open
for one week following the event.

00:05:12.180 --> 00:05:16.348
Let's move forward and get this event
started so we can all take another step

00:05:16.349 --> 00:05:18.849
in our learning process
towards better inclusivity.

00:05:19.290 --> 00:05:20.290
In a few minutes,

00:05:20.489 --> 00:05:22.709
we'll introduce
our amazing keynote speaker,

00:05:23.079 --> 00:05:24.079
Vitaly Friedman.

00:05:24.390 --> 00:05:25.390
In the meantime,

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:28.889
make yourself comfortable and get
ready for 24 hours of learning.

00:05:29.700 --> 00:05:33.601
Thank you for attending
WordPress Accessibility Day 2025.
